y hour using a premium-based mechanism that compares perpetual prices to spot indices. The exchange's institutional-grade matching engine processes funding payments automatically through Sui's fast finality, typically settling within 2-3 seconds. Long positions pay shorts when funding is positive, with rates capped at ±0.75% to prevent extreme scenarios. Bluefin's order book model ensures transparent price discovery compared to AMM-based perpetual protocols."}]]}],"$Lf",["$L10","$L11","$L12"],"$L13"]}],"$L14"]}]]}]
